---
import ZhLayout from '../../layouts/ZhLayout.astro';
---

<ZhLayout
  title="关于我们 | DGSDK 史帝克"
  description="了解东莞史帝克自动化设备有限公司。成立于2013年，专注于静电消除系统、工业清洁机、自动化设备和精密CNC零件制造。"
  canonical="https://www.dg-sdk.com/zh/about"
>
  <section
    class="about-hero"
    style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(2, 1, 1, 0.28), rgba(36, 31, 31, 0.18)), url('/assets/img/about/about-us.webp') center/cover no-repeat;"
  >
    <div class="about-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container about-hero-content">
      <span class="about-hero-kicker">关于史帝克</span>
      <h1>专注可靠性的工业自动化与精密制造解决方案。</h1>
      <p>
        东莞史帝克自动化设备有限公司，专业生产静电消除系统、清洁机、自动化设备和精密加工零件，服务全球工业客户。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-intro-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-intro-grid">
        <div class="about-intro-copy">
          <span class="about-section-label">公司简介</span>
          <h2>专注品质、工程与实用工业解决方案的专业制造商。</h2>
          <p>
            史帝克（DGSDK）总部位于广东东莞，致力于为电子、SMT、显示屏制造、包装和精密生产领域的客户提供可靠产品和定制化解决方案。
          </p>
          <p>
            我们的主营业务涵盖静电消除系统、工业清洁设备、自动化系统和精密CNC加工零件。我们注重稳定性能、生产效率，以及与全球客户的长期合作关系。
          </p>

          <div class="about-intro-points">
            <div class="about-point">
              <strong>核心产品</strong>
              <span>静电消除器、清洁机、自动化设备、CNC零件</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about-point">
              <strong>制造重点</strong>
              <span>质量控制、实用工程、稳定工业性能</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about-point">
              <strong>服务目标</strong>
              <span>为长期工业合作提供可靠支持</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-image-stack">
          <img src="/assets/img/about/about-lobby.webp" alt="DGSDK 公司大厅" class="about-main-image" loading="lazy" />
          <img src="/assets/img/about/about-lathe.jpg" alt="DGSDK CNC 车床设备" class="about-float-image" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-values-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-section-heading text-center">
        <span class="about-section-label">为何选择我们</span>
        <h2>以工业可靠性为核心。</h2>
        <p>
          我们专注于制造环境中最重要的因素：一致性、效率、质量控制、快速响应和务实合作。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-values-grid">
        <div class="about-value-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/about/about-support.png" alt="技术支持" class="about-value-icon" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>专业技术支持</h3>
          <p>我们提供及时沟通与实用技术支持，助力产品选型与项目讨论。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-value-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/about/icon-delivery.png" alt="交货保障" class="about-value-icon" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>稳定交货保障</h3>
          <p>稳定的生产管理体系，支持按时交货和高效制造协调。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-value-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/about/icon-guarantee.png" alt="质量保证" class="about-value-icon" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>品质保证</h3>
          <p>注重产品一致性、检验标准和可靠的工业性能。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-value-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/about/icon-support.png" alt="长期合作" class="about-value-icon" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>长期稳定合作</h3>
          <p>我们的目标是与全球工业客户建立稳固持久的合作伙伴关系。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-products-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-section-heading text-center">
        <span class="about-section-label">业务方向</span>
        <h2>四大核心产品方向。</h2>
        <p>涵盖静电控制、清洁、自动化和精密加工的完整工业产品体系。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-business-grid">
        <a href="/zh/products/static-eliminator" class="about-business-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/static-white-bg.png" alt="静电消除系统" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>静电消除系统</h3>
          <p>离子棒、离子风机和静电控制解决方案，适用于敏感工业环境。</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/products/cleaning-machine" class="about-business-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/cleaning-machine/polarizer-cleaner.jpg" alt="工业清洁机" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>工业清洁机</h3>
          <p>适用于PCB、FPC、SMT、偏光片、LCM、背光板和光学薄膜应用的精密清洁设备。</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/products/automation" class="about-business-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/automation/product-c.jpg" alt="自动化设备" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>自动化设备</h3>
          <p>定制工业自动化系统，旨在改善工作流程、提升生产效率。</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/zh/products/precision-machined-parts" class="about-business-card">
          <img src="/assets/img/precision-machined-parts/precision-bearing-bracket-cnc-milled.jpg" alt="精密加工零件" loading="lazy" />
          <h3>精密加工零件</h3>
          <p>具有稳定公差控制和可靠制造质量的高精度CNC零件。</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-gallery-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-section-heading text-center">
        <span class="about-section-label">工厂展示</span>
        <h2>真实的生产环境。</h2>
        <p>真实设备、真实制造、真实工业工作条件。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-gallery-grid">
        <div class="about-gallery-item item">
          <img src="/assets/img/about/about-machining-center.jpg" alt="加工中心设备" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-gallery-item item">
          <img src="/assets/img/about/about-lobby.webp" alt="DGSDK 公司大厅" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-gallery-item">
          <img src="/assets/img/about/about-lathe.jpg" alt="CNC 车床设备" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-gallery-item">
          <img src="/assets/img/about/about-cnc-process.jpg" alt="CNC 加工过程" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .about-values-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 22px;
    }
    .about-value-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .about-value-icon {
      width: 84px;
      height: 84px;
      object-fit: contain;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 0 18px;
      opacity: 0.92;
    }
    .about-gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 22px;
    }
    .about-gallery-item {
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #f7f8fa;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 36px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }
    .about-gallery-item img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 320px;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      border-radius: 18px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 991px) {
      .about-values-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-values-grid, .about-gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .about-value-icon { width: 72px; height: 72px; }
      .about-gallery-item img { height: 240px; }
    }
  </style>

  <section class="about-timeline-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-section-heading text-center">
        <span class="about-section-label">发展历程</span>
        <h2>与工业客户共同成长。</h2>
        <p>聚焦工程能力、制造可靠性和长期服务价值的发展道路。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-timeline">
        <div class="about-timeline-line"></div>

        <div class="about-timeline-item left">
          <div class="about-timeline-dot">01</div>
          <div class="about-timeline-card">
            <h3>公司成立</h3>
            <p>2013年在东莞成立，专注于工业设备、自动化和实用制造解决方案。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-timeline-item right">
          <div class="about-timeline-dot">02</div>
          <div class="about-timeline-card">
            <h3>产品扩展</h3>
            <p>扩展至静电消除系统和精密清洁设备，服务电子和显示屏行业。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-timeline-item left">
          <div class="about-timeline-dot">03</div>
          <div class="about-timeline-card">
            <h3>制造能力提升</h3>
            <p>提升CNC加工和自动化集成能力，支持更多定制化工业需求。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-timeline-item right">
          <div class="about-timeline-dot">04</div>
          <div class="about-timeline-card">
            <h3>全球合作</h3>
            <p>以稳定品质、工程支持和长期合作服务海外市场客户。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-cta-box">
        <div class="about-cta-copy">
          <span class="about-section-label">与我们合作</span>
          <h2>正在寻找可靠的工业制造合作伙伴？</h2>
          <p>联系史帝克，讨论您的项目需求、产品要求或定制工业解决方案。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-cta-actions">
          <a href="/zh/contact" class="about-cta-btn primary">联系我们</a>
          <a href="/zh/products" class="about-cta-btn secondary">查看产品</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ZhLayout>
